sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Feishu as 飞书机器人
    participant Web as Web 工作站
    participant CA as 渠道适配层<br/>(Channel Adapter)
    participant BFF as BFF 网关
    participant Router as Router 路由大脑
    participant Worker as 无状态 Worker
    participant StateDB as StateDB<br/>(Redis + MySQL)

    Note over Feishu,StateDB: 入站路径：飞书用户发送消息

    Feishu->>CA: POST /callbacks/channel/feishu<br/>{ open_id, chat_id, text }
    CA->>CA: 1. 校验 X-Lark-Signature
    CA->>CA: 2. 查 mao_channel_account 获取 user_id
    CA->>CA: 3. 查 mao_channel_session 获取 session_id<br/>(不存在则自动创建)
    CA->>Feishu: 立即返回 HTTP 200 (3s 内)
    CA->>BFF: 转换为标准 OmniMessage<br/>POST /chat/completions (内部调用)

    BFF->>Router: 分发意图
    Router->>Worker: 分配无状态 Worker 执行
    Worker->>StateDB: 加载任务快照 (若有)
    Worker->>Worker: ReAct 推演...

    Note over Worker,StateDB: 每步推演结束后 Append-only 写入 StateDB

    Worker->>StateDB: 追加写入执行步骤快照

    alt 需要用户确认 (VIEW 技能)
        Worker->>CA: 输出标准 CardSchema<br/>{ message_type: CARD, card_schema: {...} }
        Worker->>StateDB: 序列化状态快照，Worker 线程销毁
        CA->>CA: 根据 channel_type 翻译卡片格式
        CA->>Feishu: 调用飞书 OpenAPI 发送 Interactive Card
        Feishu->>CA: 用户点击卡片按钮<br/>POST /callbacks/channel/feishu/card-action
        CA->>BFF: 转换为 POST /chat/action/execute
        BFF->>Worker: 分配新 Worker，从 StateDB 恢复快照
        Worker->>StateDB: 加载状态快照，恢复执行现场
    else 直接返回结果
        Worker->>CA: 输出 OmniMessage { message_type: TEXT }
        CA->>Feishu: 调用飞书 OpenAPI 发送文本消息
    end

    Note over Web,StateDB: 入站路径：Web 用户发送消息（对比参考）

    Web->>BFF: POST /chat/completions (SSE)
    BFF->>Router: 分发意图
    Router->>Worker: 分配无状态 Worker 执行
    Worker->>StateDB: 读写快照 (Append-only)
    Worker->>CA: 输出 OmniMessage
    CA->>Web: SSE event: message / action_card
